title: Lucta (The)
body: Two newspapers were published under this title, the first on February 11, 1888, and the publication ended on July 1, 1894, with issue number 319, and the second on January 5, 1896, with 26 issues, the last of which was on June 28 of the same year.

1888: Start of the publication of the first newspaper under this title
1894: End of the publication of the first newspaper under this title
1896: Start of the publication of the second newspaper under this title
